headline: Chicago Woman Is Second Case to Be Confirmed in U.S., the C.D.C. Says
abstract: Federal health officials are monitoring 63 other people in 22 states for signs of infection.
lead_paragraph: A second patient in the United States has been found to be infected with the Wuhan coronavirus, the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention announced on Friday.
